    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to another bowl along with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>chilli oil</strong></p><p>Pick your<strong> basil leaves </strong>from their stems, discard the stems</p><p>Chop your<strong> cherry tomatoes </strong>in half</p><p>Wash your<strong> salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1598436577760-x200.jpg",
